{"tid":1125030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解 深圳人 有特權「一週一行」來香港？","createTime":"2019-04-25T12:02:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T16:28:17.000Z","uid":226548,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c12dfa587c80b898ba0be31725889bcb085ac482","tid":1125030,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T12:02:06.000Z","msg":"深圳人：一週一行<br />\n廣東 及 自由行開放省份：三個月兩次<br />\n其他大陸人：跟團<br />\n<br />\n深圳政府咁有bargaining power<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42e618a12479563dd868f60323a0a30c34615454","tid":1125030,"uid":156363,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T12:09:44.000Z","msg":"一周一行<br />\n指的是中國廣東省深圳市戶籍居民在一年內可52次赴香港自由行的政策，只需要100元簽注費用就可以享受一年內52次訪港；該政策在2015年4月13日 起生效[1]。 梁振英:深圳赴港&quot;一周一行&quot;針對內地水客。  2017年7月1日起，一周一行簽注費降低為80元。  <br />\n<br />\n而家大陸人仲可以網上申請，唔使親身去辦理，如果拎到商務簽注可以無限次數訪港。"},{"pid":"83c72aef0e16837d5c07694b703995d285c72736","tid":1125030,"uid":27369,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T12:11:57.000Z","msg":"因為唔係 香港<br />\n係  中國香港"},{"pid":"33cfafd5f4f90f28a539ae60c31df5f05056d6ab","tid":1125030,"uid":39326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c12dfa587c80b898ba0be31725889bcb085ac482","tid":1125030,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T12:02:06.000Z","msg":"深圳人：一週一行<br />\n廣東 及 自由行開放省份：三個月兩次<br />\n其他大陸人：跟團<br />\n<br />\n深圳政府咁有bargaining power<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T12:16:32.000Z","msg":"有錢咪有POWER"},{"pid":"e31977c3b3ebdf15d3e0d9e74be8111a168c906e","tid":1125030,"uid":79410,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T12:20:07.000Z","msg":"其實好多人有商務簽。<br />\n我識10個有7，8個都係商務簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4b93a0bf61ca6741618655eb58bee0dc25b5541","tid":1125030,"uid":21378,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":